annotationA: 40S ribosomal protein S2; Has a specific developmental role during oogenesis and a general role in protein synthesis as a component of the small ribosomal subunit
annotationB: Ribosomal protein L6, isoform B; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitotic spindle elongation; centrosome organization; translation; centrosome duplication; mitotic spindle organization
